{"tid":1482192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［8。18］倫敦巴黎近2000人聲援反送中抗爭 親中示威者踩場喝罵","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T04:18:02.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1db441aed0f8f819c29518cd6131c66bec766f28","tid":1482192,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190818/large/1566069033_ec5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190818%2Flarge%2F1566069033_ec5c.jpg&h=fddacd55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190818/large/1566069033_71fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190818%2Flarge%2F1566069033_71fa.jpg&h=6913850b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190818/large/1566069033_bf3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190818%2Flarge%2F1566069033_bf3a.jpg&h=03f76d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190818/large/1566069035_693c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190818%2Flarge%2F1566069035_693c.jpg&h=614fc6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球多個城市自周五起，都有集會聲援香港的反送中抗爭。在倫敦，約2000名集會人士高舉譴責香港警察濫暴的標語，從特拉法加廣場（Trafalgar Square）經唐寧街首相府遊行至白廳(Whitehall)，途中遇到一批激烈的親中示威者，不但向他們大聲叫罵，又高舉標語指他們是「賣國賊」。<br />\n<br />\n聲援港人的集會人士，高舉寫著「英國會要求中國遵守給予香港自由的承諾嗎？」、「約翰遜會向中國投降嗎？」及「我唯一想要胡椒的地方是我的湯麵」等標語，由特拉法加廣場起步，但在納爾遜紀念柱(Nelson's Column) 與一批親中示威者相遇，他們當中包括小孩，揮舞著紅色中國國旗，拿著「賣國賊」、「一個中國」和「香港永遠屬於中國的」標語，與撐港人士對罵。倫敦警方在現場戒備，以防雙方發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有出席集會、正在英國工作的港人Jack表示，今次活動與過往的明顯分別，是有非常多本土白人支持香港人，人數遠超過往的活動，部份人比港人更激動，甚至會主動走向親中示威群眾前大聲理論。另外， Jack認為親中示威者前來騷擾，卻讓整場示威活動加強了氣勢，並史無前例地吸引到很多外國記者前來，變相為港人「助攻」。</span><br />\n<br />\n而在法國巴黎，亦有約50人集會聲援反送中抗爭的示威者，他們高叫「香港自由」甚至「中國自由」的口號，一名示威者的標語卡寫著「今日香港、明日亞洲、後日歐洲」。示威者中有香港人、台灣人和大陸人。<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，現場亦有另一批中國示威者揮舞著中國國旗、譴責「香港暴徒」的暴力。他們人數比撐港示威者還多一倍。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/法新社/本報記者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190818/59944452?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59944452%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=7bec6e69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59944452%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=8ac1c07a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190818/59944452?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"}]}